 445:Drivers/lvgl/src/core/../misc/lv_style.h ****  * Instead use `lv_style_set_<prop_name>()`. E.g. `lv_style_set_bg_color()`
 446:Drivers/lvgl/src/core/../misc/lv_style.h ****  * @param style pointer to style
 447:Drivers/lvgl/src/core/../misc/lv_style.h ****  * @param prop the ID of a property (e.g. `LV_STYLE_BG_COLOR`)
 448:Drivers/lvgl/src/core/../misc/lv_style.h ****  * @param value `lv_style_value_t` variable in which a field is set according to the type of `prop`
